  <name>Dune 3D</name>
  <summary>Parametric 3D CAD</summary>

  <description>
    <p>Dune 3D is a parametric 3D CAD application. With Dune 3D you can:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Sketch and constrain in 2D and 3D</li>
        <li>Add chamfers and fillets</li>
        <li>Import STEP models for referencing them</li>
        <li>Export high-quality STEP and STL files</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

